ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectThe Greater Moncton Chamber of Commerce/La Chambre de commerce de de Grand Moncton (New-Brunswick) ** Change of name **
PrecisOrder approving the application by THE GREATER MONCTON CHAMBER OF COMMERCE/LA CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE GRAND MONCTON, in New-Brunswick, to CHANGE ITS NAME to "The Chamber of Commerce for Greater Moncton/La Chambre de Commerce pour le Grand Moncton."
